profileText: a Representative from Florida; born in Winter Haven, Polk County, Fla., July 13, 1980; A.A., Florida State College, Jacksonville, Fla., 2005; B.S., American Military University, Charles Town, W. Va., 2010; United States Army; defense contractor; business owner; security advisor; elected as a Republican to the One Hundred Eighteenth Congress (January 3, 2023–present).
